                <h4 data-uuid="630452a8a50e458894f37c1e94e9c9d6">Main Idea</h4>
                <p class="main-idea" data-uuid="36aa6b5c109a4054986b20c079b6d005">Congress approved many new programs during the Hundred Days.</p>
                <h2 data-uuid="067c63b7b87d40f1a7ef27c97376e2d0">The Hundred Days
                    <!--
                        C(&#65533;&#65533;?
                    -->
                </h2>
                <div class="yellow-star-yellow-bar" data-uuid="5f00b77f20eb4fad8a2032b0bbcc04f0"></div>
