                            <p class="pullquote_address" data-uuid="bcab96796f53403d87f242def3d0e458">—Franklin Roosevelt,<br />
                            </p>
                            <p class="p_source" data-uuid="a456db62ed294081b8e7795706ab23ef">First fireside chat radio address, March 12, 1933<i></i></p>
                        </div>
