        <p data-uuid="dc8ef253283f45c1a738ea07e2d65ffb">The National Industrial Recovery Act (NIRA) addressed business concerns. It eliminated unfair competition among companies. This law was passed with support from Secretary of Labor <dfn title="Perkins, Frances">Frances Perkins</dfn>, the nation’s first woman cabinet member.<br />
        </p>
